## 7. ESPACEMENTS & GRILLE

### Syst√®me de Grille 8pt

**Base : 8px**  
Toutes les marges, paddings et dimensions sont des multiples de 8.

|Nom  |Valeur|Usage                                   |
|-----|------|----------------------------------------|
|`xs` |4px   |Espacements tr√®s serr√©s (ic√¥nes, badges)|
|`sm` |8px   |√âl√©ments li√©s (label + input)           |
|`md` |16px  |Standard (padding cartes, gaps)         |
|`lg` |24px  |S√©paration de sections                  |
|`xl` |32px  |S√©paration majeure (entre modules)      |
|`2xl`|48px  |Marges d‚Äô√©cran, sections importantes    |

### Marges d‚Äô√âcran

```css
/* Mobile */
padding-x: 16px;
padding-y: 20px;

/* Tablet (>768px) */
padding-x: 24px;

/* Desktop (>1024px) */
padding-x: 32px;
max-width: 1200px;
margin: 0 auto;
```

### Gaps entre √âl√©ments

```css
/* Liste serr√©e (avatars, tags) */
gap: 8px;

/* Liste standard (cartes) */
gap: 16px;

/* Sections */
gap: 24px;
```

-----

## 8. RESPONSIVE DESIGN

### Breakpoints

|Device     |Min Width|Max Width|Layout                                     |
|-----------|---------|---------|-------------------------------------------|
|**Mobile** |‚Äî        |767px    |1 colonne, navigation bottom bar           |
|**Tablet** |768px    |1023px   |2 colonnes, navigation side bar optionnelle|
|**Desktop**|1024px   |‚Äî        |3 colonnes, navigation side bar fixe       |

### R√®gles Responsive

**Mobile First**  
Tous les styles de base sont pour mobile. On ajoute progressivement pour √©crans plus grands.

```css
/* Base (Mobile) */
.grid {
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
}
```

-----

## 9. NAVIGATION & STRUCTURE D‚Äô√âCRAN

### Bottom Navigation Bar (Mobile)

**Position :** Fixe en bas, toujours visible  
**Height :** 64px + safe-area-inset-bottom  
**Items :** 4 max (Dashboard, Groupes, √âv√©nements, Profil)

```css
.bottom-nav {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 64px;
  background: #FFFFFF;
  box-shadow: 0px -2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
  padding-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom);
  z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  color: #B2BEC3;
  transition: color 0.2s ease;
}

.nav-item.active {
  color: #FF6B6B;
}

.nav-item.active .icon {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}
```

### Side Navigation (Desktop)

**Width :** 240px fixe  
**Position :** Fixed left  
**Contenu :** Logo, Navigation principale, Groupes favoris, Profil

