## 10. √âTATS INTERACTIFS

### Hi√©rarchie Visuelle des √âtats

|√âtat              |Traitement visuel                           |
|------------------|--------------------------------------------|
|**Default**       |Opacit√© 100%, couleur normale               |
|**Hover**         |Transform translateY(-2px), shadow augment√©e|
|**Active/Pressed**|Transform scale(0.98), shadow r√©duite       |
|**Focus**         |Outline 2px Coral Spark, offset 2px         |
|**Disabled**      |Opacit√© 50%, cursor: not-allowed, grayscale |
|**Loading**       |Skeleton animation ou spinner               |

### Focus States (Accessibilit√©)

```css
*:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid #FF6B6B;
  outline-offset: 2px;
  border-radius: inherit;
}

button:focus-visible {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.2);
}
```

