## 12. DARK MODE (Phase 2+)

### Palette Dark Mode

|√âl√©ment         |Light    |Dark     |
|----------------|---------|---------|
|Background      |`#F7F9FC`|`#1A1D21`|
|Surface (cartes)|`#FFFFFF`|`#25292E`|
|Text Primary    |`#2D3436`|`#E8EAED`|
|Text Secondary  |`#636E72`|`#9AA0A6`|
|Divider         |`#DFE6E9`|`#3C4043`|

**R√®gle :** En Dark Mode, les couleurs brand (Coral Spark) restent identiques pour coh√©rence.

```css
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --bg: #1A1D21;
    --surface: #25292E;
    --text-primary: #E8EAED;
    --text-secondary: #9AA0A6;
  }
}
```

-----

## 13. PERFORMANCE & OPTIMISATION

### Images & Assets

**Format :** WebP avec fallback JPG/PNG  
**Lazy Loading :** Toutes images below-the-fold  
**Avatars :** Compression aggressive, taille max 200√ó200px

### CSS

**Critical CSS :** Inline dans `<head>` pour first paint  
**CSS Modules :** Pour √©viter conflits de noms  
**Purge CSS :** Enlever classes inutilis√©es en production

### Animations

**GPU Acceleration :**

```css
.animated-element {
  will-change: transform;
  transform: translateZ(0);
}
```

**Reduce Motion :**

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

